.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來而家警察家長係家長，普通學生家長就唔係家長。而家警察家長係有特權既。<br />\n如果係咁，不如掛番個警察仔女既牌係身上，以後球場使用者就唔會望住佢黎射<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對大家都好，你話係咪呀，哈姆太朗&hellip;ᘛ⁐̤ᕐᐷ"},{"pid":"9640aa9c9e1eb0e421833f3bc4c655fa48e81886","tid":1831021,"uid":114580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35773090ae2f66fbdb2285be239a8292489d99e2","tid":1831021,"uid":230759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"拎去整貼紙，A4size 慢慢cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎啲放去文宣channel得架啦，有心人會自己做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗自己cut㗎 影印鋪會幫你做埋"},{"pid":"26be9b1b4cdf805b0051040a7e2634c3c2ccc339","tid":1831021,"uid":270532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d67ca137a3496d00e717344c6a4969bf9078d643","tid":1831021,"uid":114580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"以流動連儂牆攻陷藍絲：微博肺炎截圖周圍貼<br />\n<br />\n自己人只會信自己人，文宣再靚，藍絲只會睇都唔睇就撕，但如果係簡體蝗語，點都睇哂甚至會拎返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理想 size</strong>: a5-a6<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理想張貼地點</strong>：巴士站，晨運公園欄杆，老人捉棋地方，路燈，公共交通工具椅背，酒樓等位處，街市外圍，中港旅遊巴車身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHQL2Pv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHQL2Pv.jpg&h=d69b86ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tTqinR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tTqinR.jpg&h=cbca4fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/og91A9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fog91A9w.jpg&h=c96c49d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4EpyWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4EpyWc.jpg&h=9745ea98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4go2kBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4go2kBc.jpg&h=3983d18b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NcuK2T.png\" data